headline: Phillips Edison & Company, Inc. (PECO) Q1 FFO and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Phillips Edison & Company (PECO) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of 3.17% and 2.35%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
